#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn1.79"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.79:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.79:0.2"
msgid "8. Chetvāvagga "
msgstr "8. Incinerated "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.79:0.3"
msgid "79. Pātheyyasutta "
msgstr "79. Provisions "

#. HTML: </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn1.79:1.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsu bandhati pātheyyaṃ, "
msgstr "“How should provisions be tied up? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:1.2"
msgid "kiṃsu bhogānamāsayo; "
msgstr "What’s the lair of wealth? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:1.3"
msgid "Kiṃsu naraṃ parikassati, "
msgstr "What drags a person around? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:1.4"
msgid "kiṃsu lokasmi dujjahaṃ; "
msgstr "What in the world is hard to give up? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:1.5"
msgid "Kismiṃ baddhā puthū sattā, "
msgstr "What are many beings tied up with, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:1.6"
msgid "pāsena sakuṇī yathā”ti. "
msgstr "like birds in a snare?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn1.79:2.1"
msgid "“Saddhā bandhati pātheyyaṃ, "
msgstr "“Provisions should be tied up with faith. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:2.2"
msgid "sirī bhogānamāsayo; "
msgstr "Glory is the lair of wealth. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:2.3"
msgid "Icchā naraṃ parikassati, "
msgstr "Desire drags a person around. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:2.4"
msgid "icchā lokasmi dujjahā; "
msgstr "Desire in the world is hard to give up. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:2.5"
msgid "Icchābaddhā puthū sattā, "
msgstr "Many beings are tied up with desire, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.79:2.6"
msgid "pāsena sakuṇī yathā”ti. "
msgstr "like birds in a snare.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
